Appendix item 15: Evidence Principle 2. Every customer-facing packet is a derived view over authoritative immutable evidence. Redaction cannot alter the original record. Include this context when reasoning about tradeoffs, state transitions, operator responsibilities, evidence retention, and rollout risk.

